Review Title: A nice historic place at the end of the road
Review: First time i saw a literal end of the road site. Amazingly beautiful place. The travel maybe far but it's worth it. There is only one restaurant in the area, i suggest to bring food and drinks to be sure.
Underdevelop but I love it as it is. According to the locals, there are dolphins and whales fronting the parolas. There is no amenities yet but it is a great place to have an adventure.
